Integration with cgit (webUI for dist-git):

    $ sudo dnf install cgit
    $ sudo echo "scan-path=/var/lib/dist-git/git/" >> /etc/cgitrc
    $ vim /etc/cgirc # and comment out line with `cache-size` configuration.

See this about how to configure DistGit itself: 
- https://github.com/release-engineering/dist-git
